olved in the product life cycle. Frontenders work closely with designers, testers, business analysts, and backenders. Therefore, effective and respectful communication is important to us.<br><br><strong>What we offer</strong></p> <ul> <li>Social benefits package</li> <li>Friendly and experienced colleagues, supportive and caring management</li> <li>Fully Remote or office-based work. Currently we have comfortable and conveniently located offices in Serbia, Armenia, and Kazakhstan</li> <li>Reimbursement for professional development courses and English courses</li> <li>Flexible hours, provided that you work 40 hours a week</li> <li>All the necessary equipment will be provided</li> </ul> <p>We will help with your relocation, if needed.</p> <p><strong>Come and join us in building the future!</strong></p> <ul> </ul></div>\n        <div class=\"tmpl_hh_benefits\">\n            <b class=\"tmpl_hh_title\">Что получают сотрудники</b>\n            <div class=\"tmpl_hh_items tmpl_hh_flex\">\n                <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item\">\n                    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/249576.svg\" class=\"tmpl_hh_item_icon__img tmpl_hh_fix\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"tmpl_hh_item__text\">Помощь с релокацией</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item\">\n                    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/249577.svg\" class=\"tmpl_hh_item_icon__img\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"tmpl_hh_item__text\">Компенсация английского </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item\">\n                    <div class=\"tmpl_hh_item__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"https://hhcdn.ru/ichameleon/249578.svg\" class=\"tmpl_hh_item_icon__img\" alt=\"\">\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"tmpl_